<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="importance-n">importance <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪm'pɔːtns/    美 /ɪm'pɔːrtns/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>重要 (性)；重大：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>attach importance to</strong>
对…重视</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He had finally understood <strong>the importance of</strong> my work. 
他终于理解了我工作的重要性。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As we all know, friendship is <strong>of great importance</strong> to everyone. 
众所周知，友谊对每个人都很重要。</p></div></div>